modules.description: This module defines a query type for representing HTTP requests and provides functions to create and format mock API backends. It works with string-based routes and headers, along with expected input-output pairs for testing. Concrete use cases include simulating HTTP endpoints during unit tests and validating request structure and responses in a controlled environment.
